messages.subject: Re: [samuraihistory] request information on yumi bow
messages.msgSnippet: Hi! You may want to contact Don Szymanski of the Ryuko Kyudojo in Boulder, Colorado.  I know that he spent a number of years in Japan learning to make bows.
messages.messageBody:
Hi!

You may want to contact Don Szymanski of the Ryuko Kyudojo in Boulder,
Colorado. I know that he spent a number of years in Japan learning to make
bows. The dojo website may even have some links to books. Also try:

www.zenko.org

Shannon
